name: Outside Inside Freestyle Delta Kite
description: Bring the freedom of a kite with you on your next hike or picnic. The Freestyle Delta Kite catches the wind easily and soars to smile-inducing heights. The compact design is easy to pack and weighs next to nothing.Made from ripstop nylon with fibreglass poles.Single line is easy to control and rolls up into a comfortable ring handle.Stabilizing tail keeps the kite soaring freely.Designed for winds from 9 to 32kph.Dimensions: 56 x 30 x 6cm, collapsed: 35 x 12 x 3cm.Includes: 30m of braided line, a winder and a carry bag.
